@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/board
@testUrl = http://localhost:8080/test/board

### 기존 - 성공
GET {{baseUrl}}/1
Accept: application/json

### 기존 - 실패
GET {{baseUrl}}/99
Accept: application/json

### 공통응답 - 성공
GET {{testUrl}}/1
Accept: application/json

### 공통응답 - 실패
GET {{testUrl}}/99
Accept: application/json
